name: Kwasi One-Niner
description:
A piece from the collection of characters in the upcoming Graphic Novel Series, Veil Of The Gods.

Kwasi One-Niner. Nadine Granie is an outlaw with a conscience. In the past she’s been focused on overturning the established hierarchy, but lately she’s had her life shaken up. In the aftermath of a violent shoot-out that saw the death of her partner-in-crime, Nadine has decided she needs to upgrade at any cost.
